
TY  - JOUR
T1  - Adaptive Heuristics
AU  - Hart, Sergiu
Y1  - 2005/09/01
PY  - 2005
DA  - 2005/09/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1468-0262.2005.00625.x
